(15, 5, '2014-04-27 16:26:20', '2014-04-27 16:26:20', '<p style="color: #000000">With hints of cinnamon and nutmeg, our carrot cupcake has a mosit spiced carrot sponge with a delicious orange cream cheese buttercream, decorated with a sugar carrot. This flavour is popular with all ages. Please note our carrot cupcakes do not contain nuts, but they do contain raisins. This flavour is very popular all year round, and is available in our bakeries every day, or to order online now.</p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<div id="AddToBasket" style="color: #000000"></div>', 'Carrot Cupcake', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'carrot-cupcake', '', '', '2014-04-27 16:26:20', '2014-04-27 16:26:20', '', 0, 'http://cardiganbasket.co.uk/localbakery/?post_type=product&#038;p=15', 0, 'product', '', 0),
