(329, '_transient_wdpun_project_details_237', '<p>Tired of being bogged down with theme options? We''ve got you covered with the easiest setup you''ve ever seen in a theme!</p>\n<p>From the all-star theme designer behind the GridMarket theme and the WPMU.org redesign, SimpleMarket is as elegantly designed as it is powerful under the hood. It gets rid of all the bulky theme options, favoring an easy setup with an exquisite look right out of the box! With full <a href="http://premium.wpmudev.org/project/e-commerce">MarketPress</a> support, creating an e-Commerce site is easier than ever before!</p>\n<p>SimpleMarket is the ultimate, easy to set up MarketPress theme you''ll ever see and it works perfectly well for regular WordPress sites too!</p>\n<p>But lacking options doesn''t mean it''s lacking any punch!\nTake a look at the powerful features built into this simple theme!</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>HTML5</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Responsive design</strong> that easily adapts to a variety of screen sizes and devices</li>\n<li>Full support for <strong>Post Formats</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Editor style</strong> support means your posts will look the same in your editor as when they''re displayed on the front-end</li>\n<li>Built in <strong>MarketPress styl&hellip;</strong></li>\n</ul>\n', 'no');
